  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个教育系统的数据流图，核心是课堂服务（ClassroomService）和内容分发网络（ContentCDN）的交互。起点是ClassroomService，它会去请求ContentCDN。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_ClassroomService",
        "Education_ContentCDN"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，ClassroomService作为起始节点，指向ContentCDN。ContentCDN这里需要做成判断节点吗？还是普通矩形？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_ClassroomService",
        "Education_ContentCDN"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "ContentCDN要做成菱形判断节点，因为分发结果有成功和失败两种分支。成功的话走GradeSync，失败的话要回写到StudentDB。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_ContentCDN",
        "Education_GradeSync",
        "Education_StudentDB"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，ContentCDN做成菱形，分出两条带标签的线：Success指向GradeSync，Failure指向StudentDB。GradeSync之后呢？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_ContentCDN",
        "Education_GradeSync",
        "Education_StudentDB"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "GradeSync处理完要回到ClassroomService，形成闭环。然后ClassroomService再连到LMS_Portal，进入策略评估环节。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_GradeSync",
        "Education_ClassroomService",
        "Education_LMS_Portal"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "策略评估是一个独立的子模块吗？我需要用subgraph包起来。",
